In this chapter, you will create some important metrics for your inventory

3
00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:14.800
analysis, and you will be introduced to a classification technique known as ABC analysis.

4
00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:14.800


5
00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:14.800


6
