At this stage, you will be focusing on the analysis and visualization part.

7
00:00:19.520 --> 00:00:24.520
You have already made a good start by obtaining basic calculations such as COGS,

8
00:00:24.520 --> 00:00:30.080
revenue, and profit, but you want to go a bit deeper to get more insights for your final output.

9
00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:31.000


10
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:31.000


11
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.840
And you have also found some interesting insights.

12
00:00:33.840 --> 00:00:33.840


13
