14
00:00:33.840 --> 00:00:38.640
There are 104 items within five categories, for which decoration and jewelry

15
00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:44.480
categories have the highest average costs of goods sold per item of around five dollars.

16
00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:44.480


17
00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:45.120


18
00:00:45.120 --> 00:00:52.120
Home and accessories had the largest profit in 2020, reaching an amount of up to $110,000.

19
00:00:52.120 --> 00:00:52.120


20
00:00:52.120 --> 00:00:52.120


21
